Title: Honoring Alice M. Barnes as recipient of the Women's History Award by the 79th Precinct Community Council, Inc. and the Brooklyn Club, NANBPWC, Inc.
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION honoring Alice M. Barnes upon the occasion of her designation as recipient of the Women's History Award by the 79th Precinct Community Council, Inc. and the Brooklyn Club, NANBPWC, Inc.
